## E. Styling (SLD)

Contoh SLD untuk layer kawasan:
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<StyledLayerDescriptor version="1.0.0">
  <NamedLayer>
    <Name>oikn:kawasan</Name>
    <UserStyle>
      <FeatureTypeStyle>
        <Rule>
          <RasterSymbolizer>
            <PolygonSymbolizer>
              <Fill><CssParameter name="fill">#3b82f6</CssParameter></Fill>
              <Stroke><CssParameter name="stroke">#1d4ed8</CssParameter></Stroke>
            </PolygonSymbolizer>
          </RasterSymbolizer>
        </Rule>
      </FeatureTypeStyle>
    </UserStyle>
  </NamedLayer>
</StyledLayerDescriptor>
```
